content: wtfsayo: Focused on a broad range of improvements and fixes, including significant work on CLI tooling and infrastructure as evidenced by PRs like elizaos/eliza#5599 "fix: improve bunx detection and remove npm references in CLI" and elizaos/eliza#5586 "feat: improve cli ci tests + migrate to bun native process sp...", alongside general bug fixes and maintenance across the codebase. Their primary focus areas were other work, bug fixes, and tests, with significant changes in configuration and test files.
